      "category": "concept",
      "year": null,
      "description": "A t-shirt depicting Null Island — the mythical point at 0°N 0°E where data with missing or zeroed-out coordinates mysteriously \"lands\". Designed and printed by someone at Mapzen, the beloved open-source mapping company.",
